sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Browser
    participant JavaScript
    participant Server
    
    User->>Browser: Enter note text and click Save
    Browser->>JavaScript: Form submit event triggered
    JavaScript->>JavaScript: e.preventDefault() - stop page reload
    JavaScript->>JavaScript: Create note object with content & date
    
    Note right of JavaScript: Update UI immediately<br/>(no waiting for server)
    JavaScript->>Browser: Add note to notes array
    JavaScript->>Browser: Redraw notes list (DOM manipulation)
    Browser->>User: Show new note immediately
    
    JavaScript->>Server: POST /new_note_spa (JSON data)
    activate Server
    Server->>Server: Save note to memory
    Server-->>JavaScript: 201 Created
    deactivate Server
    
    Note right of Browser: Page never reloads!<br/>Only 1 HTTP request made